units metal
atom_style atomic
boundary p p p

# Create fcc copper box
lattice fcc 3.615
region box block 0 5 0 5 0 5
create_box 1 box
create_atoms 1 box
mass 1 63.546

# Define potential
pair_style pace
pair_coeff * * current_extended_potential.yace Cu   # replace with your actual filename

# Simulation settings
neighbor 2.0 bin
neigh_modify delay 5

velocity all create 300.0 12345 mom yes rot no dist gaussian

fix 1 all nvt temp 300.0 300.0 0.1
thermo 100
thermo_style custom step temp pe ke etotal press
run 1000 # file is currently incomplete: i need to understand a lot more about Cu structures to develop an intuition of what to test. 
